{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add France to countries where expats receive Winter Fuel Payment",
        "additional_details": "This is because the calculation of average temperatures in France takes into account temperatures of France's overseas departments, meaning temperatures are higher compared to the UK. I think this is an unfair policy, and just a way of saving the government money.",
        "background": "I would like France to be re-added to the list of countries where expats receive the winter fuel allowance. France is not on the list of countries where people are eligible. \r\n \r\n",
